                <h1 class="ui header">The Technologies</h1>
                <p>
                   The application is primarily based around the Raspberry Pi, and the TP-Link Kasa Smart Plug series. The programs are written in Python, making use of the
                   python-kasa library to control the plug.
                 <p>  The mobile application is delivered through Blynk while allows for the data to be viewed, and push notifications to be sent.</p>
                  <p> ThingSpeak's MQTT protocol is used to get temperature data to display in chart form on the web application.</p>
